extends layout

block content
  .content
    h1 Balance Report
    p
      if user
        a(href='/user')=user.name
        |, your current balance is: 
        strong=balance
    p
      | This is your transaction history:
    table(border='1')
      tr
        each key in Object.keys(expenses[0])
          th
            strong=key
      each expense in expenses
        tr
          each key in Object.keys(expense)
            td=expense[key]
    p Don't spend to much.